icial and user made campaigns! </strong><br></li><li> <strong>Download </strong>user made maps from the Steam Workshop!<br></li><li> <strong>Create </strong>new maps &amp; campaigns in the map &amp; campaign editors!<br></li><li> <strong>Share </strong>your own custom maps &amp; campaigns with the community!</li></ul>",
